source.physicalDescription: 1 print : lithograph, printed in orange, green and white ; sheet 57.7 x 43.2 cm
notes.contents: The poster evokes the colours of the Indian flag: saffron, white and green that symbolize sacrifice, truth, and prosperity

Meridian Ad Systems, Cochin (concept) lAshraya, the AIDS Awareness and Counselling Centre, a Project of IMA Blood Bank 1998 lAshraya, the AIDS Awareness and Counselling Centre, a Project of IMA Blood Bank India 10/07/2009 see http://imacochin.org for IMA (Indian Medical Association UkLW UK Transcription from the item
source.lettering: Your nation needs you. Your family needs you. Don't let AIDS drive you to an early grave. Creative Concept: Meridian Ad Systems, Cochin. Includes telephone numbers. Bears AIDS red ribbon logo (for lAshraya). The IMA is the Indian Medical Association
